# Status report layout and PDF

- **Single source of truth:** The only place to change layout or styling for both preview and PDF export is `components/StatusReportView.tsx`. The PDF is produced by client-side capture of that view (html2canvas + jsPDF in `lib/statusReportPdfCapture.ts`).
- Do not add a separate PDF-only layout or component. Any visual change must be made in StatusReportView so preview and exported PDF stay identical.
